1. *Opasni* psi su pobjegli iz azila. (Dangerous dogs have escaped from the shelter.)
2. Moraš biti *opasan* ako želiš da preživiš u ovom gradu. (You have to be dangerous if you want to survive in this city.)
3. Oni su bili vrlo *opasni* kriminalci prije nego što su uhvaćeni. (They were very dangerous criminals before they were caught.)
4. Ova oblast je poznata po *opasnim* putevima koji prolaze kroz planine. (This region is known for its dangerous roads that pass through the mountains.)
5. Ljudi koji se bave ekstremnim sportovima su obično skloni *opasnim* situacijama. (People who engage in extreme sports are usually prone to dangerous situations.)
6. *Opasan* je put do vrha planine, ali pogled s tamošnjeg vidikovca je nezaboravan. (The road to the top of the mountain is dangerous, but the view from the lookout point there is unforgettable.)
7. Policija je upozorila građane da budu oprezni zbog *opasnih* terorističkih prijetnji. (The police warned citizens to be careful because of dangerous terrorist threats.)
8. Opasnost od eksplozije je bila toliko *opasna* da su morali evakuirati cijelu četvrt. (The danger of an explosion was so dangerous that they had to evacuate the entire neighborhood.)
9. Ovaj sport je pun *opasnih* elemenata, ali je i jako uzbudljiv. (This sport is full of dangerous elements, but it is also very exciting.)
10. Ne možeš biti siguran u svoju sigurnost u ovom *opasnom* kraju grada. (You can't be sure of your safety in this dangerous part of the city.)